{
  "stem": "1537.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I looked-- SS with the German shepherds.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And yelling, with the sticks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they're opening the freight train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they chased, us. 'Raus!' Everybody was completely confused.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three, four days, locked in there, no food-- you were already dehumanized.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were like a zombie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't know if you are alive or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we jumped down, the train, you know, down to the floor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I'm trying to keep the family together-- my father, my sister, my brother, then my little sister and my little nephew.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm trying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't work like this, because the SS came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They start to beat the hell out of everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hit over the head.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just 'Raus!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Raus!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Schnell!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Schnell!'",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of a sudden, you know, I'm losing everyone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father is to the right.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my brother, Betzalel is to the left of me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I see my little sister yelling to my father, 'Father!",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wait for me!' But he couldn't because they were beating him up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my little nephew, he was two-and-a-half years old is saying [INAUDIBLE] Wait for me!' I'm watching, the baby's crying.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they're beating the hell out of everybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, this is-- I cannot take it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm dying!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[SOBBING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in two minutes, I don't see my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't see my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't see nobody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing is I see-- I hold my hand for my brother, Joseph.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, let's not get separated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's hold together, please.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when Father goes away, [? imagine, ?] he still had enough power in him to tell my brother, Joseph, Betzalel, please watch over Hershel, because I was the young one, you know.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were frightened because he knew that I do things.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
